Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 10/05/2025

1. Introduction
Welcome to Christian Singles Connect! Your privacy matters to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information. By using Christian Singles Connect, you consent to the practices described here.

2. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:
• Personal Information: Includes details like your name, email address, gender, date of birth, religious affiliation, and profile data provided during registration.
• Usage Data: Information about your device, app usage patterns, and log details.
• Location Data: With your permission, we gather location information to help filter matches based on proximity.

3. How We Use Your Information
Your data is used to:
• Provide faith-based matchmaking services and improve your user experience.
• Customize app features to suit your preferences and values.
• Ensure your contact information is kept private and secure.

4. Your Rights as a User
• You can request to delete your account and associated data at any time through the "Delete Account" feature in the app.
• You can also access and update your personal information within the app settings.

5. Data Security
We employ advanced encryption and other security protocols to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or misuse.

6. Contact Us
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please reach out to us at ChristianSinglesConnect@ChristianSinglesConnect.com or weezardinc@gmail.com.
